{"tid":1570212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"資訊已經太混亂 我地要團結就需要一本抗爭手冊做聖經","createTime":"2019-09-15T03:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T03:29:06.000Z","uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d390882f5a974ad040ba8252fd8133d82702d39","tid":1570212,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"200萬人 唔係個個上連登<br />\n就算上都唔會跟得切所有野<br />\n好多人因為資訊太混亂<br />\n唔知點解 唔知點算 唔知點做<br />\n我地應該出版一本手冊<br />\n包含所有人都應該知既野<br />\n保證到所有野都確實可靠<br />\n<br />\n印刷一本幾十頁既精華書<br />\nA6 SIZE 然後派畀所有人<br />\n<br />\n不單教大家可以做乜野<br />\n同點解要咁做<br />\n仲可以放係袋入面袋住旁身<br />\n<br />\n目前衹係寫左少少實用資訊<br />\n好多唔同既野未寫<br />\n加入<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JABufk663yTdXdU7ErWQhQ]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJABufk663yTdXdU7ErWQhQ%5D&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=d7cad328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JABufk663yTdXdU7ErWQhQ]</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pi8SOcX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpi8SOcX.jpg&h=495225cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNRJarh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNRJarh.jpg&h=b5dba074&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfLt5ZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfLt5ZD.jpg&h=9b82a4f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbEbjjD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcbEbjjD.jpg&h=c98acdb2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBNPQri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBNPQri.jpg&h=ad412083&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUVazSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUVazSZ.jpg&h=354079a8&s={SIZE}\" /> [img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/FF8CZjE.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg